{"tid":2372760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原有線中國組正式退場 請大家支持眾新聞中國組","createTime":"2021-01-20T03:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:46:28.000Z","uid":147376,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eddb9b83d8d9c0669283f05adda14e5ffc172829","tid":2372760,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2809431759201292&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2809431759201292%26id%3D265944843550009&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=9655588d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2809431759201292&amp;id=265944843550009</a><br />\n<br />\n自2013年5月我們在此建立「有線中國組」專頁後，至今接近8個寒暑，多年來，各位提出很多有益建議，鼓勵我們努力前行，中國組成員內心充滿感謝之情，為有此高質素的讀者和觀眾而自豪。<br />\n<br />\n自今日起，原有中國組成員會退出這個專頁，另有發展，之前在此發佈的報道將會繼續保留，再次多謝大家的愛護。<br />\n<br />\n司徒元  黃麗萍  黃慧茹  徐文傑<br />\n翁維愷  王寶熒  曾海琪  林杰倫  <br />\n廖廸莎  廖樂欣  區翠恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbfAzsF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxbfAzsF.jpg&h=f5395852&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b55c15730f45de2014c90cc5b5216768f91283fe","tid":2372760,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"IG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkcnews?igshid=l9yafrvyrab1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkcnews%3Figshid%3Dl9yafrvyrab1&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=096bb930\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkcnews?igshid=l9yafrvyrab1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e7a00693\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\